<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Theatre</td></tr>
<tr id="L1"><td><a href="#L1">1</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: On stage, a velvet-clad arm raises a bloody knife, then plunges it again into his sleeping victim. The audience are rapt.</td></tr>

<tr id="L2"><td><a href="#L2">2</a></td><td>KIRK:  Interesting. An Arcturian Macbeth.</td></tr>

<tr id="L3"><td><a href="#L3">3</a></td><td>LEIGHTON:  (a man with an eyepatch) Watch him. Watch Macbeth.</td></tr>

<tr id="L4"><td><a href="#L4">4</a></td><td>LENORE:  (as Lady M) Is he dead? Speak. Is King Duncan dead?</td></tr>

<tr id="L5"><td><a href="#L5">5</a></td><td>KARIDIAN:  Will all great Neptune's ocean wash this blood clean from my hands.</td></tr>

<tr id="L6"><td><a href="#L6">6</a></td><td>LEIGHTON:  That voice. He's back. That man on the stage. I'm certain of it. That's Kodos the Executioner.</td></tr>

<tr id="L7"><td><a href="#L7">7</a></td><td>KARIDIAN:  Pluck out mine eyes!</td></tr>

<tr id="L8"><td><a href="#L8">8</a></td><td>SOMEONE: Captain's log, star date 2817.6. Starship Enterprise diverted from scheduled course. Purpose, to confirm discover by Doctor Thomas Leighton of an extraordinary new synthetic food which would totally end the threat of famine on Cygnia Minor, a nearby Earth colony.</td></tr>

<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Leighton's home</td></tr>
<tr id="L9"><td><a href="#L9">9</a></td><td>KIRK:  You mean to tell me you've called me three light years off my course just to accuse an actor of being Kodos?</td></tr>

<tr id="L10"><td><a href="#L10">10</a></td><td>LEIGHTON:  He is Kodos. I'm sure of it.</td></tr>

<tr id="L11"><td><a href="#L11">11</a></td><td>KIRK:  You said you discovered a new food concentrate. What am I supposed to put in my log, that you lied? That you diverted a starship with false information? You're not only in trouble, you've put me in trouble, too.</td></tr>

<tr id="L12"><td><a href="#L12">12</a></td><td>LEIGHTON:  I did it to trap Kodos!</td></tr>

<tr id="L13"><td><a href="#L13">13</a></td><td>KIRK:  Kodos is dead.</td></tr>

<tr id="L14"><td><a href="#L14">14</a></td><td>LEIGHTON:  Is he? Is anyone sure? A body burned beyond recognition?</td></tr>

<tr id="L15"><td><a href="#L15">15</a></td><td>KIRK:  Tom, the authorities closed the book on that case years ago.</td></tr>

