<tr id="L20"><td><a href="#L20">20</a></td><td>LEIGHTON:  Well, I'm not. I remember him. That voice. The bloody thing he did.</td></tr>

<tr id="L21"><td><a href="#L21">21</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: He turns his head to reveal it's not just an eyepatch, but a covering over half his face</td></tr>

<tr id="L22"><td><a href="#L22">22</a></td><td>LEIGHTON:  Jim, Jim, I need your help. There were only eight or nine of us who actually saw Kodos. I was one, you were another. If he's to be exposed,</td></tr>

