<tr id="L345"><td><a href="#L345">345</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: The Ghost summons Hamlet</td></tr>

<tr id="L346"><td><a href="#L346">346</a></td><td>HAMLET:  Whither wilt thou lead me? Speak, I'll go no further.</td></tr>

<tr id="L347"><td><a href="#L347">347</a></td><td>SOMEONE: KARIDIAN Mark me.</td></tr>

<tr id="L348"><td><a href="#L348">348</a></td><td>HAMLET:  I will.</td></tr>

