<tr id="L359"><td><a href="#L359">359</a></td><td>RILEY:  I know that voice, that face, I know it. I saw it. He murdered them.</td></tr>

<tr id="L360"><td><a href="#L360">360</a></td><td>KARIDIAN:  Thy soul, freeze thy young blood.</td></tr>

