<tr id="L391"><td><a href="#L391">391</a></td><td>LENORE:  You cannot deny him his last performance!</td></tr>

<tr id="L392"><td><a href="#L392">392</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: She grabs the security guard's phaser and runs out onto the stage</td></tr>

<tr id="L393"><td><a href="#L393">393</a></td><td>KARIDIAN:  Lenore, don't!</td></tr>

